{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.length","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/length","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><em><code>length</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem\"><code>removeItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Storage API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a> インターフェイスの読み取り専用プロパティ <code>length</code> は、<code>Storage</code> オブジェクトに保存されているデータアイテムの数を表す整数を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var aLength = storage.length;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"戻り値","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>整数</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の関数はカレントドメインのローカルストレージに 3 個のデータアイテムを追加して、ストレージ内のアイテムの数を返します:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'yellow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'cats.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 3 を返す</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 実際の例として、<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/web-storage-demo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a> をご覧ください。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>仕様書</th>\n      <th>策定状況</th>\n      <th>コメント</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n